{"tid":1804454,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蝗式經濟圈 vs 黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-12-31T04:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T11:40:21.000Z","uid":310867,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adc5e1638e8e56691d558c1e7d2afdf30db2a3bf","tid":1804454,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"發現<br />\n<br />\n蝗式經濟圈在於大量支國人湧入各國瘋搶，不論係潮牌服飾、家庭電器、奶粉藥品，甚或廁所板，無一不歡<br />\n<br />\n本著我消費你受惠既觀念，最鐘意一篋篋周遊列國，不論港日韓台都有其身影<br />\n<br />\n當然經常湧入港係為購奶粉，大量去走水貨圖利，令到本港BB要捱貴奶粉，係為咗咩要落嚟？質量實好過大陸買多多聲，起碼無咁易變大頭，無咁易買到假貨。而事實上，利潤唔太高都照走，為既都係普遍正貨，仲話唔係靠佢地落嚟帶動消費，香港人完蛋了<br />\n<br />\n仲有炒黃牛賣假貨都係支國人拿手好戲，就唔明而家黃色經濟圈側重於品質、良心，賣既商品唔平，但至少係憑良心良知去經營，唔會同國內有太大利益衝突，唔需要顧慮太多別國人既感受<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈可以體現自由經濟，消費者自由選擇幫襯返價值觀相近既商舖，亦都令到唔少人去返一啲自己過往不曾幫襯過既小店，而唔係貪方便去連鎖，提升返小店喺地區既存在感，守望相助，亦係我地需要減少依賴大集團連鎖式規範統一化商品服務。至少，黃色經濟圈商舖，各有特色，互相競爭，先可以吸引人去感受本區人小本經營式札根於當地既熱情服務，來得更有人性化更親切<br />\n<br />\n咁問香港人<br />\n<br />\n你想要影響市容呢一種？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mR9FpyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmR9FpyH.jpg&h=e0033fe7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n定還是<br />\n<br />\n自律自覺支持捍衛本土意識既呢一種？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cTzRwdX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcTzRwdX.png&h=6cdae099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"18f8ecf3362e9f63c9f460a00863793194ab9145","tid":1804454,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:15:24.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=2bd674bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=702024fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要24000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=0550b0d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>美國聯署</ins> deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">3/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要6000人 </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhelp-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=8615489d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/help-congress-act-mass-genocide-uighur-muslims-china</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">deadline fighters 請出招</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379607859d2feac0b414fe1a61d89064e42fdf45","tid":1804454,"uid":144626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"蝗式經濟圈＝藥房、金鋪"},{"pid":"9d4378bba42142bf343e907ff53be9f8c4ebb5c0","tid":1804454,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu